        <body>
            <p>
                <add>שלום ארדוף לידידי האלוף כש"ת אין כמה' איבן עבר נ"רי</add>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Cinc.</placeName>
                <date>July 14<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5614</date>. A M.</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Rev. Sir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">According to my Promise, I send<lb/> You the newborn Israelite; it
                was <hi rend="underline">born</hi><lb/> &amp; <hi rend="underline">delivered</hi> to
                its <hi rend="underline">94</hi> Aborments on the <add>פרש' חקת ובלק</add><lb/>
                    (<add>שבת קדש</add>) &amp; sold <hi rend="underline">on the streets</hi> by the
                Newspapers Boys<lb/> among others, on the same Day &amp; <date>Sunday</date>
                enst—among<lb/> the <sic>Gentils</sic> to preat<add>?</add> abroad <add>חילול
                    השם</add>;—Sir, You will be<lb/> amazed by reading a Jewish history in it—<lb/>
                (:Le premier Chef-D'oeuvre:) containing a <sic>discription</sic><lb/> which can only
                be expected of an <hi rend="underline"><persName>Eisenmenger</persName></hi><lb/>
                united with the entirely <hi rend="underline">Ignorance</hi> of our<lb/> Rabbinical
                Laws &amp; Cassuites, (over a <add>משומד</add> (as he discribes<add>?</add>:)<lb/>
                needs not to be send <add>סעודת הבראה</add>—nor has a brother or<lb/> sister to
                mourn <add>שבעת ימים</add>—neither is necessary to keep<lb/> you &amp; to say
                    <add>עם קדוש</add> or learn a <add>שעור</add> as he means it.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">The whole shows <del><add>?</add></del> evidently his Attention<lb/>
                to abuse our rabbinical Laws &amp; to make our<lb/> holy Religion ridiculous in the
                sight of the <sic>Gentils</sic><lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">using</hi> every <hi rend="underline">means</hi>, even
                    <add>שקרים</add> &amp; absurdity!—<lb/> this is his only Happy—he is a <add>אומר
                    להכעיס</add> in<lb/> the real sense of the word—next more—</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">I remain, Dr. Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Your most obdt &amp; respect<add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <persName role="author">Dr. J. Mayer</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
